{"title":"[變數宣告]Var vs let ","date":"2020-02-22T08:37:35.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 22, 2020","L":"02/22/2020","MM-DD":"02-22"},"link":"2020/02/22/variable","tags":["JS","W3HEXSCHOOL"],"updated":"2020-06-18T16:56:16.634Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>…</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"JavaScript語法\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/02/22/variable#JavaScript語法\"></a>JavaScript語法</h1>\n<p>這次要介紹的語法主要是宣告變數:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>let</li>\n<li>var</li>\n<li>const</li>\n</ol>\n<p>在介紹上述3個宣告之前我們要先介紹何謂<font color=\"red\">作用域（Scope）</font></p>\n<p>我先慣把作用域分成<font color=\"blue\">全域變數(Global Variable)</font>和<font color=\"blue\">區域變數(Local Variable)</font>兩種</p>\n<h2 id=\"全域變數-Global-Variable\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/02/22/variable#全域變數-Global-Variable\"></a>全域變數(Global Variable)</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1iySPkH.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>假設我們的程式主要有3個功能</p>\n<p>A-function(求圓形面積)</p>\n<p>B-function(求球形面積)</p>\n<p>C-function(求圓錐面積)</p>\n<p><strong>3個功能互相獨立而且不相依</strong></p>\n<p>3個方程式計算時必須共同要用到<font color=\"red\">Pi=3.14159</font>這個變數，而<font color=\"red\">Pi</font>就是所謂<font color=\"blue\">全域變數(Global Variable)</font></p>\n<p>全域變數的<strong>特性</strong>用一句話來表示就是：<mark><em>牽一髮而動全身</em></mark></p>\n<p>以下圖為例：</p>\n<p><strong>Pi=3.14159</strong> 變成 <strong>Pi=3</strong>時，下面3個function都會跟著一起變動<br>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rbeHzly.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"區域變數-Local-Variable\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/02/22/variable#區域變數-Local-Variable\"></a>區域變數(Local Variable)</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aUKIdQO.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>假設3個function中有各自的變數</p>\n<p>分別為<strong>apple</strong>，<strong>banana</strong>，<strong>cup</strong></p>\n<p>3個變數只能各自存活在各自的function中，而且不同的function不能存取不是自己的變數</p>\n<p>在JS中我習慣把<strong>區域變數</strong>的作用範圍（Scope）分成兩類 <font color=\"red\">function</font>內部 以及<font color=\"red\">{大括弧}</font>內部</p>\n<p>[補充]：作用在{大括弧}內部就是所謂的作用在<font color=\"blue\"><strong>block</strong></font>內</p>\n<h2 id=\"Var宣告-vs-let宣告\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/02/22/variable#Var宣告-vs-let宣告\"></a>Var宣告 vs let宣告</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><font color=\"blue\">Var宣告</font>就是作用在<font color=\"red\">function</font>內部</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">testVar</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple = <span class=\"string\">'蘋果'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"literal\">true</span>) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> apple = <span class=\"string\">'香蕉'</span>;<span class=\"comment\">// 蘋果即將被香蕉取代</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(apple);  <span class=\"comment\">// 香蕉</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\">testVar();</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><font color=\"blue\">let宣告</font>就是作用在<font color=\"red\">{}</font>內部</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">testLet</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> apple = <span class=\"string\">'蘋果'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"literal\">true</span>) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> apple = <span class=\"string\">'香蕉'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 這裡的 apple = '香蕉' 只有在if括號內部作用，離開括號就沒有作用了</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(apple);<span class=\"comment\">//banana</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    }<span class=\"comment\">//if</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(apple);  <span class=\"comment\">// apple</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">}<span class=\"comment\">//function</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">testLet();</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dTsR0G7.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Const宣告\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/02/22/variable#Const宣告\"></a>Const宣告</h2>\n<p><font color=\"blue\">Const宣告</font>就是宣告一個<font color=\"red\">常數</font>（<strong>儘量不要更動的定值</strong>）</p>\n<p>Const宣告時一定要給它一個值而不能只給它變數名稱，不然會報錯喔！！！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K62WT2Y.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</body></html>","prev":{"title":"[CodingStyle]命名規則","link":"2020/02/29/CodingStyle-命名規則"},"next":{"title":"[編譯器]Compiler VS Interpreter","link":"2020/02/16/compiler"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/02/22/variable/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"JavaScript語法","index":"1","children":[{"title":"","id":"全域變數-Global-Variable","index":"1.1"},{"title":"","id":"區域變數-Local-Variable","index":"1.2"},{"title":"","id":"Var宣告-vs-let宣告","index":"1.3"},{"title":"","id":"Const宣告","index":"1.4"}]}]}